106
00:08:45,352 --> 00:08:47,229
Oh, come on.

107
00:08:47,229 --> 00:08:50,190
When have you ever not lived like that?

108
00:08:50,190 --> 00:08:52,401
Still, you did the right thing.

109
00:08:52,401 --> 00:08:56,071
- I mean, this is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity.
- You're right.

110
00:08:56,071 --> 00:08:58,198
