Morning!

117
00:10:27,287 --> 00:10:30,374
I'm going for a run around Inokashira Park.

118
00:10:30,374 --> 00:10:32,125
Inokashira Park?

119
00:10:32,125 --> 00:10:36,129
You know, it's actually much bigger than it seems.

120
00:10:36,129 --> 00:10:38,765
- Do you want to come?
- No way.

121
00:10:53,355 --> 00:10:55,023
<i>When I run,</i>

122
00:10:55,023 --> 00:10:58,451
<i>I am surrounded by the ever-changing scenery.</i>

123
00:11:01,905 --> 00:11:03,831
<i>And I like that.</i>

124
00:11:04,866 --> 00:11:07,585
<i>It feels like I'm not just stuck in a rut.</i>

125
00:11:08,954 --> 00:11:11,089
<i>It feels like...</i>

126
00:11:11,707 --> 00:11:14,509
<i>I'm moving forward with each passing day.</i>

127
00:11:22,676 --> 00:11:25,012
Have you looked into
what you want to study

128
00:11:25,012 --> 00:11:27,430
