with your academic path.

138
00:11:53,373 --> 00:11:55,500
I'll do my best to help you out.

139
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:58,177
I will. Thank you.

140
00:11:58,962 --> 00:12:00,380
Thank you so much.

141
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:01,923
It's my pleasure.

142
