- I am.

184
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:26,063
I lived in Japan for five years
when I was in elementary school.

185
00:16:26,063 --> 00:16:28,698
So, communication won't be a problem.

186
00:16:31,193 --> 00:16:33,987
And you'll obviously be good at Japanese

187
00:16:33,987 --> 00:16:35,781
since you're a literature major.

188
00:16:35,781 --> 00:16:37,457
Yes, sir.

189
00:16:38,950 --> 00:16:41,119
Not only am I good at Japanese,

190
00:16:41,119 --> 00:16:42,788
but I can speak Korean, too.

191
00:16:42,788 --> 00:16:46,291
So I can serve Korean customers.

192
00:16:46,291 --> 00:16:49,503
We do get a lot
of Korean tourists these days.

193
00:16:49,503 --> 00:16:51,512
Can you speak Korean?

194
00:16:52,839 --> 00:16:55,349
No, I can't speak Korean.

195
00:16:59,137 --> 00:17:00,514
However,

196
00:17:00,514 --> 00:17:02,849
I've had to work to pay for my tuition,

197
00:17:02,849 --> 00:17:05,018
so I have a lot of experience.

198
00:17:05,018 --> 00:17:07,604
I need the money
to pay for this semester, too.

199
00:17:07,604 --> 00:17:09,447
That must be tough.

200
00:17:12,859 --> 00:17:16,530
I need to find work so I can make money

201
00:17:16,530 --> 00:17:20,117
to pay for rent each month,
or I'll end up getting kicked out.

202
00:17:20,117 --> 00:17:22,285
And I'm here in Japan all by myself.

203
00:17:22,285 --> 00:17:23,704
Rent...

204
00:17:23,704 --> 00:17:25,789
Yeah, the rent is pretty high around here.

205
00:17:25,789 --> 00:17:27,416
It really is!

206
00:17:27,416 --> 00:17:30,033
And since I'm an overseas student,

207
00:17:30,033 --> 00:17:33,002
I can't even apply for a loan.

208
00:17:34,381 --> 00:17:36,842
All right, I've heard enough.

209
00:17:36,842 --> 00:17:38,719
So, you need money to pay your rent,

210
00:17:38,719 --> 00:17:41,013
and you need money for school.

211
00:17:41,013 --> 00:17:42,139
Unfortunately,

212
00:17:42,139 --> 00:17:44,774
