213
00:17:48,312 --> 00:17:50,272
How about we do it like this?

214
00:17:50,272 --> 00:17:53,658
Why don't you stay for tryouts today?

215
00:17:55,569 --> 00:17:58,279
I'll keep an eye on how you two work

216
00:17:58,279 --> 00:18:00,698
and hire the one who does better.

217
00:18:00,698 --> 00:18:02,626
That's fair, isn't it?

218
00:18:02,626 --> 00:18:05,387
All right. Let's do this.

219
