223
00:18:17,799 --> 00:18:19,926
- Thank you.
- Thank you so much.

224
00:18:19,926 --> 00:18:22,179
Here you go. One large ramen.

225
00:18:22,179 --> 00:18:24,389
- I'll bring you your rice, too.
- Here you go.

226
00:18:24,389 --> 00:18:26,065
Thank you.

227
00:18:28,560 --> 00:18:29,936
Thank you for waiting.

228
00:18:29,936 --> 00:18:31,605
- I brought the noodles!
- I got it.

229
00:18:31,605 --> 00:18:33,231
One al dente shoyu ramen, ready to serve!

230
00:18:33,231 --> 00:18:35,450
I'm on it. Thank you.

231
00:18:37,861 --> 00:18:39,029
Thank you for waiting.

232
00:18:39,029 --> 00:18:40,322
This way, please.

233
00:18:40,322 --> 00:18:43,825
- Thank you, ma'am.
- Thank you. The food was really good.

234
00:18:43,825 --> 00:18:45,953
Thank you for waiting.

235
00:18:45,953 --> 00:18:48,087
Thank you for waiting.

236
00:18:53,794 --> 00:18:56,512
- Welcome!
- Welcome!

237
00:18:58,090 --> 00:18:59,724
Hey! Menu!

238
00:19:02,719 --> 00:19:04,353
Here you go, sir.

239
00:19:07,516 --> 00:19:10,811
This is our <i>tonkotsu shio</i> ramen,

240
00:19:10,811 --> 00:19:13,939
and this is our <i>tonkotsu shoyu</i> ramen.

241
00:19:13,939 --> 00:19:17,567
The <i>tonkotsu shio</i> ramen is our best seller.

242
00:19:17,567 --> 00:19:21,454
Please take your time
and let me know when you've decided.

243
00:19:25,450 --> 00:19:28,753
Is there a waiter who speaks Japanese here?

244
00:19:30,330 --> 00:19:33,000
How may I help you, sir?

245
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:36,169
