to speak Japanese properly.

250
00:19:51,852 --> 00:19:53,903
Sir, I'm going to have to ask you

251
00:19:54,479 --> 00:19:57,106
to apologize for what you just said.

252
00:19:57,106 --> 00:19:58,275
What?

253
00:19:58,275 --> 00:19:59,776
You want me to apologize?

254
00:19:59,776 --> 00:20:01,820
Yes, sir.

255
00:20:01,820 --> 00:20:04,072
Please apologize.

256
00:20:04,072 --> 00:20:06,582
I'll take your order once you do.

257
00:20:07,220 --> 00:20:09,522
